        148.42417112849222
      ],
      "parameters": {
        "color": 7,
        "width": 493.289385759178,
        "height": 418.29352785836636,
        "content": "## 2. 创建新文档以记录RFP问题回复\n[详细了解如何使用Google Docs](https://docs.n8n.io/integrations/builtin/app-nodes/n8n-nodes-base.googledocs/)\n\n针对每个处理的RFP，我们将创建专属文档来存储回复结果。该文档将作为RFP回复的草稿文件使用。"
      },
      "typeVersion": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "2b3df6af-c1ab-44a1-8907-425944294477",
